   CIRCUS-KALEIDOSCAPE (Houston) _ The new $10 million circus
called Barnum's Kaliedoscope is making its way across the country
during a 50-week tour. Critics are raving about the show, and in
many cities, runs have been extended. By PAMELA MITCHELL.
