   RUSSIA-TALBOTT (Moscow) _ As Russian forces continue to pound
rebel positions in the breakaway region of Chechnya on Thursday,
Deputy Secretary of State Strobe Talbott accused Russia of
violating ``international norms'' by treating civilians as
