<P>
   MIDEAST-CHRISTMAS _ BETHLEHEM, West Bank _ Following Christmas
Eve in Bethlehem, the centerpiece of the millennium milestone the
world marks this year. Will include color from the day, from the
crowds gathering at the mosque for noon prayers at one side of
Manger Square, to the Midnight Mass in the Church on the other side
and the Protestants in the Shepherds Fields nearby. Developing.
(Kaplow, Cox News Service) WITH PHOTOS
