   INTERNATIONAL
</P>
<P>
   MIDEAST-BETHLEHEM _ BETHLEHEM, West Bank _ The ``little town''
has not had so much at stake for centuries. Amid $200 million in
badly needed construction, Bethlehem is ready to host a Christmas
Eve that could attract 50,000 people and make the case the the city
is ready to pull itself out of decades of turmoil to become a
spiritual center. Developing. (Kaplow, Cox News Service). 20. WITH
