Bombardieri. 1000 words.
</P>
<P>
   FBI-INDICTMENT (Boston) _ Although federal prosecutors say the
investigation into wrongdoing by FBI agents is still alive in the
wake of the indictment of retired star agent John Connolly, any
probe will be hampered by the five-year statute of limitations. By
Shelley Murphy. 800 words.
</P>
<P>
   CONCAVE-CHEST (Boston) _ Doctor at Massachusetts General uses a
tool similar to an automotive dent puller to treat a condition
known as sunken chest. Procedure is minimally invasive, doc says.
By Richard Saltus. 850 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   NASDAQ-RECORD (Undated) _ It's a Merry Christmas on Wall Street
as the Nasdaq composite index tops 4000 less than two months after
passing 3000. Venerable Dow Jones also on track to hit its first
record close since August. By Ronald Rosenberg. 900 words.
</P>
