   GERMANY-INDUSTRY (Frankfurt, Germany) _ In a move that sent
Germany's stock market soaring, the government endorsed plans
Thursday to untangle the web of cross-ownership in German companies
that have defined their structure since the end of World War II. By
Edmund L. Andrews.
</P>
<P>
   With graphic.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 8:30 p.m. ET.)
