   &UR; UPS  &LR; _ The ``e'' drops out of e-commerce around 1 a.m. as
thousands and thousands of packages arrive at the United Parcel
Service processing center in South San Francisco. Although volume
at this and other UPS facilities nationwide peaked earlier, the
