Lazarus
</P>
<P>
   &UR; COOKEXPRESS &LR;  _ CookExpress, which whips up ready-to-cook
gourmet meals for Internet customers, has suspended operations
until next year, when it ``hopes to complete a key round of
funding.`` The temporary shutdown during what should be its busiest
time of the year highlights how unprepared many e-commerce sites
were to deal with an onslaught of holiday shoppers. By Kelly Zito
</P>
</TEXT>
