<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-23 22:10 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8024 &Cx1f; taf-z
s f BC-BIZ-MIDSTREAM-$ADV26-     12-23 0744
